    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1913-10-07T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1913-10-06T00:00:00-05:00" n="1357"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d1357">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 817.51/578.</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Minister for Foreign Affairs of
                            Nicaragua</gloss> to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                        State</gloss>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram—Translation.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Managua</hi>
                        </placeName>; <date
                            ana="#date_undated-inferred-from-document-content-and-sibling-dates"
                            calendar="gregorian" notAfter="1913-10-07T23:59:59-05:00"
                            notBefore="1913-10-06T00:00:00-05:00">
                            <hi rend="italic">undated</hi>
                        </date>
                        <hi rend="italic">; received October 7, 1913</hi>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>The President wishes to express through me to your excellency his heartfelt
                    thanks for your beneficient and efficient cooperation in the adjustment of the
                    new loan contracts that have won his approval and that of the Assembly of
                    Nicaragua.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Diego M. Chamorro</hi>.</signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
